### Environment / Secrets ###
# The REAL application.properties contains the live MySQL password and
# JWT signing secret — it must never be committed to a public repo.
# Only application.properties.example (with placeholder values) is
# tracked in git; anyone cloning this repo copies that file to
# application.properties and fills in their own real values locally.
src/main/resources/application.properties
application-local.properties
application-secrets.properties
